            <p class="bold">Course Enrollment Deadline</p>
            <p>The deadline to enroll for the courses in Spring 2025 is February 27. Please ensure you have registered before this date.</p>
            <span class="announcement-date">Posted: January 15, 2025</span>
        </div>
        <div class="announcement-item">
            <p class="bold">Updated Campus Policies</p>
            <p>Please review the updated campus policies regarding health and safety protocols for the upcoming semester.</p>
            <span class="announcement-date">Posted: January 10, 2025</span>
        </div>
        <div class="announcement-item">
            <p class="bold">Scholarship Applications Open</p>
            <p>Applications for merit-based scholarships are now being accepted until March 1st.</p>
            <span class="announcement-date">Posted: January 5, 2025</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>